main event: A piece of hollow metal was found on a farm in Essex, Illinois by a granddaughter and sent for analysis.
interesting points: The object is hollow and somewhat square in shape., The object was found while walking in a field., It was kept in possession before being sent for analysis., A letter from the Air Force stated they are not experts on the matter., The Air Force suggested contacting the Office of the Secretary of the Air Force for further information.
witness description: the granddaughter who found the object
